headline: 3 Reasons HCA Has Explosive Upside Potential
summary: Since July 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 93.6%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, HCA Healthcare has surged 245% to $362.60 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 13.9% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 9.7%.
